data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom home with a fully fenced in backyard and a deck.  Over 2500 sq ft in a prime Avon location!  The open kitchen/family room floorplan inside flows right out to the huge private deck, making this home perfect for entertaining. The 4th bedroom is HUGE and can easily be a bonus room.  The master features vaulted ceilings with dual walk-in closets.  New AC unit, 2 stage furnace, ecobee smart thermostat installed in 2021.  Water softner stays and RO drinking water system. Seller is offering to pay up to $6,500.00 in buyer's closing cost!
